<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>입시정보 - 코딩앤플레이</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/board-layout.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/career.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <div class="board-layout-container">
        <%- include('partials/sidebar', { currentView: 'admission-info' }) %>

        <div class="board-main-content">
            <div class="career-container">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                    <h4 class="fw-bold m-0 text-dark">
                        <i class="bi bi-file-text me-2 text-primary"></i>입시정보
                    </h4>
                </div>

                <div class="row g-4">
                    <!-- 입시 가이드 -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                            <div class="card-header bg-white py-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold m-0"><i class="bi bi-book me-2"></i>입시 가이드</h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="text-muted">수시/정시 입시 전형별 가이드 및 전략 자료</p>
                                <div class="list-group">
                                    <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
                                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                            <span>📘 2026 수시 전형 가이드</span>
                                            <small class="text-muted">PDF</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
                                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                            <span>📗 정시 지원 전략</span>
                                            <small class="text-muted">PDF</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 입시 정책 -->
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-0">
                            <div class="card-header bg-white py-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold m-0"><i class="bi bi-file-earmark-ruled me-2"></i>입시 정책</h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="text-muted">교육부 및 대학별 최신 입시 정책 자료</p>
                                <div class="list-group">
                                    <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
                                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                            <span>📄 2026 대입 전형 시행계획</span>
                                            <small class="text-muted">PDF</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                    <a href="#" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action">
                                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                                            <span>📄 학생부 평가 가이드</span>
                                            <small class="text-muted">PDF</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 입시 분석 -->
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="card shadow-sm border-0">
                            <div class="card-header bg-white py-3">
                                <h6 class="fw-bold m-0"><i class="bi bi-graph-up me-2"></i>입시 결과 분석</h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p class="text-muted">주요 대학 입시 결과 분석 및 트렌드</p>
                                <div class="row g-3">
                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                        <div class="border rounded p-3 text-center">
                                            <i class="bi bi-trophy text-warning display-6 mb-2"></i>
                                            <h6 class="mb-1">SKY 입시 분석</h6>
                                            <small class="text-muted">2025년 결과 분석</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                        <div class="border rounded p-3 text-center">
                                            <i class="bi bi-mortarboard text-primary display-6 mb-2"></i>
                                            <h6 class="mb-1">의대 입시 트렌드</h6>
                                            <small class="text-muted">최근 5개년 분석</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                        <div class="border rounded p-3 text-center">
                                            <i class="bi bi-cpu text-success display-6 mb-2"></i>
                                            <h6 class="mb-1">공대/AI 학과 분석</h6>
                                            <small class="text-muted">신설 학과 중심</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
